Perry was joined on stage by Lenny Kravitz as well as Missy Elliott at the University of Phoenix Stadium.

She entered the arena riding a huge lion while singing 'roar' before going onto some of her other hits such as 'dark magic', 'I kissed a girl' and 'California girls'. 

It was at that point that female rapper Elliott surprised the crowd in Arizona before Perry ended the energetic performance by flying through the sky while singing 'firework'. 

